    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Sombra infiltrates via Translocator to Hack a key target or ultimate-holder out of position, then finishes them off with Machine Pistol while they're unable to use abilities.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Stealth breaks the instant she attacks or takes damage, and she has very low health, so any hero who spots her before the hack lands can usually kill her outright.</p>"
